## Why This Is Asked

Tests expertise in building robust streaming pipelines with real-world constraints: per-partition ordering, bounded buffers, backpressure, dynamic rebalancing, and exactly-once sinks. It also probes fault tolerance, replay semantics, and test strategy.

## Key Concepts

