- **Out-of-order tests**: Send updates out of sequence (e.g., v1, v3, v2) and confirm that v2 is buffered or dropped appropriately based on the configured policy
- **Dynamic resize tests**: Verify that no requests are lost or duplicated when the worker pool is resized at runtime
- **Integration tests**: Simulate realistic workloads with concurrent producers and consumers to validate end-to-end behavior

