- **Bounded queues and backpressure** — Prevents memory exhaustion by signaling producers when capacity is reached
- **Per-tenant fairness** — Weighted round-robin or quota-based scheduling ensures no tenant is starved
- **Dynamic worker pool resizing** — Scales workers based on queue depth and throughput requirements
